  "remarks": "Tiz Pars was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: Tiz Pars attempted to procure a five axis laser welding and cutting machine, which could make a material contribution to Iran’s missile program, on behalf of SHIG.\n\nThe Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
